des:
Eddie’s TV show is a brand new scripted feel good, clean, wholesome, character driven comedy about a fictional beach bar and grille in Venice, California, the boss Eddie, his staff and all the regulars, locals and tourists who eat there.

When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next fact. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
